  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个评论管理的状态流转图，核心是从创建到最终处理的完整生命周期。初始状态是Pending，然后可以走向Approved、Rejected或Deleted三条分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Create Comment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Pending是入口状态。那创建评论的触发点应该放在哪里？是外部系统触发进入Pending，还是Pending内部有子状态处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Create Comment",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "创建动作从Etcd集群发起，进入Pending。Pending本身是个复合状态，内部需要AwaitingModeration子状态来处理审核队列，由IngressController管理这个流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Pending设为复合状态，内部包含AwaitingModeration，IngressController负责这个子状态的入口和出口。现在处理Approved分支——审核通过后应该直接可见？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Approved也是复合状态，内部有Visible状态，由LoadBalancer承载。Visible可以编辑，编辑后回到Visible，形成循环。另外Approved也可以被删除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Delete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Approved包含Visible和Edited的循环，且Approved和Rejected都能走向Deleted。那Rejected分支怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Rejected同样用IngressController接入，内部是Hidden状态。Hidden可以添加拒绝原因（WithReason），最终归档到RedisCache。Rejected也能直接删除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Delete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Deleted的处理有点特殊——它是终态吗？我看到它要连接到LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deleted",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，Deleted确实是终态，但应该直接连到LoadBalancer做清理，不是循环回去。另外给四个主要状态加上注释：Pending标注\"评论从Pending开始等待审核\"，Approved标注\"已批准评论可见且可编辑\"，Rejected标注\"已拒绝评论隐藏且可附原因\"，Deleted标注\"已删除评论永久移除\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
